---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Terms of Service | BitGuru">
  <section class="pt-32 pb-24 px-5 sm:px-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-display font-extrabold mb-8">Terms of Service</h1>
    <div class="space-y-6 text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">
      <p>Last updated: March 2026</p>
      <p>By accessing and using the BitGuru platform, you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service. BitGuru provides educational content related to cryptocurrency and blockchain technology. All information provided is for educational purposes only and does not constitute financial advice.</p>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-on-surface pt-4">1. Educational Content Disclaimer</h2>
      <p>BitGuru courses, consultations, and materials are strictly educational. Cryptocurrency trading involves significant risk of loss. Past performance of any trading strategy or methodology does not guarantee future results.</p>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-on-surface pt-4">2. User Responsibilities</h2>
      <p>Users are responsible for their own trading decisions. BitGuru is not liable for any losses incurred from applying concepts learned through our educational materials.</p>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-on-surface pt-4">3. Intellectual Property</h2>
      <p>All course materials, videos, and content are the intellectual property of BitGuru and may not be reproduced, distributed, or shared without written permission.</p>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-on-surface pt-4">4. Refund Policy</h2>
      <p>Course purchases are eligible for a full refund within 14 days of purchase if less than 20% of the course has been completed. Consultation fees are non-refundable within 48 hours of the scheduled session.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
